snippet.title: World War 3 | Operation Skyfront Battle Pass Trailer
snippet.description:
Venture to the Bosporus Strait, connecting Europe and Asia in Operation Skyfront, the latest expansion of World War 3 available for free! Play now on the new Istanbul map, specifically on the construction site of one of the skyscrapers. Meet new operators from Turkey and across the Mediterranean. Fight with new weapons and modify them with the new Customization feature for both weapons and strikes.

Learn more about Skyfront update from our article: bit.ly/3pV2PbQ

The Battle Pass is your key to 100 tiers of exclusive rewards in Operation Skyfront. Get started today: https://worldwar3.com/skyfront

Stay up to date with all World War 3 related news:
